pointsandrectangleslab

Class APPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • pointsandrectangleslab.APPoint

  • public class APPoint
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a point of the Rectangle to be drawn in a Graphic Window. The APPoint has an x-coordinate and a y-coordinate
